Reported-by: Sergio Lopez <slp@redhat.com>
Tested-by: Sergio Lopez <slp@redhat.com>
Signed-off-by: Stefano Garzarella <sgarzare@redhat.com>
Acked-by: Jia He <justin.he@arm.com>
